body:
Bila Bobase puts out new music that will keep you in a worship mood for long. His subtle and feeble voice gives a very soulful touch to the song. Also, it is a song with a very deep revelation about the love and power of God . Do you know how to call Jesus and give Him the right attributes to His name, then you should download this song? Let this song introduce you to how great our God is. 

**Download Song in our music library** 

Watch Lyric video on [YOUTUBE ](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gKmA0lRbylE)
